1. Thank you for your tasty dinner. 2. He always waits for his brother. 3. He sent
his son for ice cream to the shop. 4. He thanked them for help. 5. She was famous
for her good voice. 6. We will call you in the evening. 7. Yesterday my grandmother
bought a washing machine. She paid for it a lot of money. 8. She was famous for her
beauty. 9. If we do not hurry up, we will be late for the train. 10. She looked for her
friend yesterday in the evening. 11. She called for matches. 12. He asked for my car
for two hours. 13. When did Kate leave for Madrid?
